---
// src/components/Faq.astro
// Trendy, accessible FAQ with soft gradients + glassy cards.
---

<section
  id="bbb-faq"
  aria-labelledby="faq-heading"
  class="relative mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-base-300/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-base-200/80 via-base-100 to-base-100 shadow-sm"
>
  <!-- Decorative blobs -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-24 -left-24 size-72 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-28 -right-24 size-72 rounded-full bg-secondary/10 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8">
    <h2 id="faq-heading" class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-5">
      What is the Big Beautiful Boycott?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-4 lg:gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Card -->
      <article
        class="group card bg-base-100/90 border border-base-300/60 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <svg class="mt-0.5 size-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 3a9 9 0 1 0 9 9A9.01 9.01 0 0 0 12 3Zm1 13h-2v-2H9v-2h2V8h2v2h2v2h-2Z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              The Big Beautiful Boycott is a nonpartisan nationwide movement reclaiming the
              power of the people through collective action. Every dollar is a choice, and by
              withholding our spending we are taking a stand for fairness, democracy, and human
              dignity – one dollar at a time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        class="group card bg-base-100/90 border border-base-300/60 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 size-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 8a4 4 0 1 1-4 4 4.005 4.005 0 0 1 4-4Zm-7 9a7 7 0 0 1 14 0v1H5Z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">How long does it last?</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                The Big Beautiful Boycott began November 1, 2025 — and it lasts until We The People
                win our seat at the table. We’ll stop when the government stops denying us a voice.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        class="group card bg-base-100/90 border border-base-300/60 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 size-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 3 2 9l10 6 10-6-10-6Zm0 8.74L5.32 8.5 12 4.26 18.68 8.5 12 11.74Z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Why is there not a list of demands?</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                There’s no list of demands because we’re not asking — we’re acting. The goal is simple:
                remove their money, remove their power. Only then will We The People have a real seat at
                the table to decide the future of our country.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        class="group card bg-base-100/90 border border-base-300/60 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 size-6 opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4 4h16v4H4zm0 6h10v10H4z"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">How does it work?</h3>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                It’s a slow burn — and we’re building power week by week. Every Saturday, 10 new
                companies make the Big Beautiful Boycott list. We provide you the reasons why and
                sources to get you started if you want to dive deeper on the “why.” The more we boycott,
                the hotter it gets for billionaires and corrupt political players.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
